	TITLE Example 7.--Organic decomposition and bubble formation
	SOLUTION 1
	EQUILIBRIUM_PHASES 1
	        Calcite
	        CO2(g)  -1.5
	SAVE solution 1
	SELECTED_OUTPUT
	        file ex7.pun
	        si CO2(g) CH4(g) N2(g) NH3(g)
	        gases CO2(g) CH4(g) N2(g) NH3(g)
	END
